cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.ET

Reasoning: 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a new measurement system for monitoring the energy demand of machines used in manufacturing. This falls under the domain of systems and control.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses automatic disaggregation methods to estimate the energy demand of constituent loads. This involves the use of machine learning techniques.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): Similar to the above, the use of automatic disaggregation methods involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper may involve the development of software for implementing the proposed measurement system and automatic disaggregation methods.
- cs.ET (Embedded Systems): The proposed measurement system may involve the use of embedded systems for monitoring the voltage and current of the aggregate load.
